description.en:
MM72 is a long-term project related to the resolution of the Non Performing Tokens problem.
An innovative SWAP promises the conversion of non-performing tokens with values from a minimum of 10 to a maximum of 100 times the ascertained value (which in MM72 can never be absolute zero).
